Install the latest version of Vagrant
	sudo dpkg -i virtualbox-4.3_4.3.12-93733~Ubuntu~precise_amd64.deb 

Install the latest version of Vagrant
	sudo dpkg -i vagrant_1.6.3_x86_64.deb

Install the latest version of ChefDK
Details at https://www.chef.io/chef/
	sudo dpkg -i chefdk_0.3.6-1_amd64.deb

Make sure Ruby has secure source for it:-
//- to remove insecure connection
	sudo gem sources -r http://rubygems.org/ 
//- add secure connection
	sudo gem sources -a https://rubygems.org/ 

Install the ruby-dev
	sudo apt-get install ruby-dev

Update gem
	sudo gem update

Install Celluloid
	sudo gem install celluloid -v '0.16.0'

Install Nokogiri
	sudo gem install nokogiri -v '1.6.5'

Install the Vagrant Berkshelf plugin:
	vagrant plugin install vagrant-berkshelf

Install the Vagrant Omnibus plugin:
	vagrant plugin install vagrant-omnibus
	
Install the Vagrant Hostmanager plugin:
	vagrant plugin install vagrant-hostmanager
